<p>I am working on a Material Property Package in Julia, for a Property Package to become a standard one is mandatory that implements different COM | CORBA interfaces for each component (<a href="http://www.colan.org/index-3.html" rel="nofollow">CAPE-OPEN standards</a>). Is it possible to implement such interfaces in Julia-Lang? </p>  <p>EXAMPLE CODE</p>  <pre><code>type MaterialObject   .   .   module ICapeCorbaInterface end  runserver(materialobject) </code></pre>